OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fdonor, says ex-MP          
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A former Tory MP claims a government   
OL,6, minister pressed her to help advance a 
OL,7, party donor seeking a knighthood or    
OL,8, peerage, court documents have revealed.
OL,10,FCharlotte Leslie told a colleague that 
OL,11,FLord Agnew - then a Cabinet Office     
OL,12,Fminister - insisted she appoint        
OL,13,Fmillionaire Mohamed Amersi as chairman 
OL,14,Fof an influential group she led.       
OL,16,FMs Leslie also claims Mr Amersi told   
OL,17,Fher such a role would help him secure  
OL,18,Fan honour, the court documents allege. 
OL,20,FMr Amersi is suing her for defamation. 
